# CLIP ChangeLog for clip-layout/baselayout-core-userpriv

*baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r7 (12 Nov 2015)

  12 Nov 2015; Piotr Chmielnicki <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r7.ebuild, -baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r6.ebuild:
  Creating directories for SSM in /var/run

*baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r6 (26 Feb 2015)

  26 Feb 2015; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r6.ebuild, -baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r5.ebuild:
  Add smartcard directory creation.

*baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r5 (18 Jan 2011)

  18 Jan 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r5.ebuild, -baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r4.ebuild:
  Make ptmx a symlink to pts/ptmx for use with multiple instances of devpts.

*baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r4 (26 Mar 2010)

  26 Mar 2010; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r4.ebuild, -baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r3.ebuild:
  Add /var/shared mount point.

*baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r3 (10 Jul 2008)

  10 Jul 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r3.ebuild, -baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Make /var/tmp a symlink to /tmp.

*baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r2 (11 Apr 2008)

  11 Apr 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r2.ebuild, -baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Add /dev/mapper.

  07 Nov 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  Remove all ebuilds before 1.0-r1.

*baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r1 (09 Jul 2007)

  09 Jul 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Replace /dev/random by a symlink to urandom, to avoid ressource
  exhaustion attacks.

*baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0 (18 Jan 2007)

  18 Jan 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-core-userpriv-1.0.ebuild:
  Initial import, moved out user priv from baselayout-clip. 
  Removed most devices, which are no longer needed now that 
  we don't chroot Xorg.
